snippet.title: JANITOR BLEEDS Official Release Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Wishlist, follow and get JANITOR BLEEDS on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1552310/JANITOR_BLEEDS/

You enter the abandoned arcade after your car has crashed, and the shelter you were looking for is trying to eat you alive in this dark mystery-horror adventure. Solve mysteries, keep JANITOR satisfied, and always be aware of what's behind your back. This is a game of your life.
